msItem.note:
Text identified by N. R. Ker. Ker described the arrangment of the leaves and text as follows: 'Fragments of bk.
                                    3. The leaves at the beginning contain parts of XI.4,5; XI,8: XII,1,2; XIV,3,4; XVI,2.3; XVII.3; XVIII.1,2;
                                    XVIII.4,5; XX.2,3. The leaf at the end has XVII.1-3 on the verso and XVIII.2-4 on the recto.'
